title: Pixel 4A 5G - Import from USA to India
content:
I am planning to import Pixel 4a 5G from US to India. I see both Pixel 4a and Pixel 4a 5G devices are having same LTE bands. I would like to get it confirmed if Indian carriers (Especially "Jio" carrier , which needs VoLTE to work) are compatible with Pixel 4a 5G. 

Thanks, 
Krishna
